{
  "description": "A stunning nighttime aerial view captures a cityscape illuminated with vibrant lights and fireworks. The iconic Bay Bridge stretches across a dark body of water, its lights creating a bright path toward the city. Buildings of varying heights, adorned with numerous lights, dominate the skyline. Above a prominent skyscraper, a burst of red and green fireworks illuminates the night sky, adding a celebratory feel to the scene. The lower portion of the image shows a shadowed landmass with dense trees and the continuation of city lights. The overall effect is a dazzling display of urban beauty and nighttime activity.",
